<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription(classicMode==True)->You've learned that a valuable relic is nearby.\n\nThe [relic_name] is one of [relicGlobalCount] ancient objects venerated by many people. If you could collect it, you could build a reliquary to make your colonists happy and attract wealthy pilgrims.</li>
    <li>questDescription(classicMode==False)->You've learned that a relic of [ideo_name] is nearby.\n\nThe [relic_name] is an ancient object venerated by all [ideo_memberNamePlural]. If you could collect it, you could build a great reliquary to make [ideo_memberNamePlural] happy, attract wealthy pilgrims, and bring more people to [ideo_name].</li>
    <li>questDescriptionPartBeforeDiscovery->First, you need to find the [relic_name]. Watch for opportunities to gather information about it.</li>
  -->
  <RelicHunt.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription(classicMode==True)->Hai saputo che una preziosa reliquia si trova nelle vicinanze.\n\nIl [relic_name] è uno dei [relicGlobalCount] oggetti antichi venerati da molte persone. Se riuscissi a ottenerlo, potresti costruire un reliquiario per rendere felici i tuoi coloni e attirare ricchi pellegrini.</li>
    <li>questDescription(classicMode==False)->Hai saputo che una reliquia di [ideo_name] si trova nelle vicinanze.\n\nIl [relic_name] è un oggetto antico venerato da tutti i [ideo_memberNamePlural]. Se riuscissi a ottenerlo, potresti costruire un grande reliquiario per rendere felici i [ideo_memberNamePlural], attirare ricchi pellegrini e portare più persone a [ideo_name].</li>
    <li>questDescriptionPartBeforeDiscovery->Per prima cosa, devi trovare il [relic_name]. Cerca opportunità per raccogliere informazioni a riguardo.</li>
  </RelicHunt.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
